post_text:
The East Hall Middle School Staff staff could have spent its lunch enjoying its break, but several members of the staff organized and carried 50 boxes of food into the community! Thank you to all East Hall Middle School Partners in Ed and staff members who made the Elf Express possible!

#EastHallHasItAll
@Hall_Schools #themostcaringplaceonearth

